text: Falsovelleda rufescens is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1970.Biolib.cz - Falsovelleda. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Acanthocinini Category:Beetles described in 1970 Category:Taxa named by Stephan von Breuning
